# @name HealthCheck
### 1. SYSTEM HEALTH CHECK (GET)
GET http://localhost:3002/
Accept: application/json

### -----------------------------------------------------------------

# @name RegisterNewUser
### 2. REGISTER A NEW USER ACCOUNT (POST)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Dang",
  "lastName": "Khoi",
  "email": "khoi.vo2026@example.com",
  "password": "mysecurepassword123"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------

# @name LoginSuccess
### 3. USER LOGIN SUCCESS (POST)
# Note: This will automatically receive and store the 'refreshToken' inside HttpOnly Cookie
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "khoi.vo2026@example.com",
  "password": "mysecurepassword123"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------

# @name RegisterValidationFailed
### 4. TEST REGISTER VALIDATION FAILURE (POST)
# Expected Result: 400 Bad Request with English Zod validation feedback
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "",
  "lastName": "Khoi",
  "email": "invalid-email-format",
  "password": "123"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------

# @name SilentRefreshSession
### 5. REQUEST NEW ACCESS TOKEN VIA SILENT REFRESH (POST)
# Note: REST Client automatically attaches the cookie from the Login step above!
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/auth/refresh
Accept: application/json

### -----------------------------------------------------------------

# @name UserLogout
### 6. USER LOGOUT / CLEAR SESSION COOKIE (POST)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/auth/logout

### -----------------------------------------------------------------

### 1. ĐĂNG NHẬP ĐỂ LẤY ACCESS TOKEN TRONG JSON BODY
# @name LoginSession
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "khoi.vo2026@example.com",
  "password": "mysecurepassword123"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### 2. TEST XEM PROFILE CÁ NHÂN (CẦN ACCESS TOKEN)
# Copy chuỗi accessToken dài ngoằng từ kết quả Login ở trên dán vào sau chữ Bearer
GET http://localhost:3002/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6Mywicm9sZSI6InVzZXIiLCJpYXQiOjE3ODI5NzkxNTEsImV4cCI6MTc4Mjk4MDA1MX0.61JMCAbEOND7mausYhFO_kvuZnyIz9fE7CqKLlKrb-A

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### 3. TEST PHÂN QUYỀN ADMIN (VỚI TOKEN USER THƯỜNG)
# Expected Result: 403 Forbidden vì tài khoản của bạn đang có role: 'user'
GET http://localhost:3002/api/v1/auth/admin-dashboard
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6Mywicm9sZSI6InVzZXIiLCJpYXQiOjE3ODI5NzkxNTEsImV4cCI6MTc4Mjk4MDA1MX0.61JMCAbEOND7mausYhFO_kvuZnyIz9fE7CqKLlKrb-A